<step>
  <title>Capture Images/Create Steps</title>
  <instructions>&lt;p&gt;There are several ways to create new steps:&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;1) Click New Step - this creates a blank step.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;2) Click Capture (you can also open the Capture Palette by clicking on the arrow next to the camera).&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;3) Turn on the Clipboard Recorder (with the Clipboard Recorder on, any image you place on the system clipboard will be added to your ScreenSteps lesson).&lt;/p&gt;</instructions>
